<white>synopsys:</>
    the command <green>use</> is used to change current website.

<white>usage: </><green>use</> <yellow>$website</>

<white>arguments:</>
    <yellow>$website</> - the website name.

<white>examples:</>
    <green>use</> <yellow>example.com</>

<white>notes:</>
    after changing the current website, some commands will be available 
    for you, like: <green>su</>, <green>useradd</>, etc.
    
    these commands require a "website context" in order to function 
    properly.